The '''Bomerwrights of Sullest''' were a group which constructed [[Lightsaber/Legends|laser swords]]. [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Starkiller]] gave [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] a [[chrome]] handled sword made by them following their arrival at [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]].

